snippet.title: FUFUFU - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Have you ever raced with sheeps, poked noses, or battled against pirate cats? 
Welcome to FUFUFU, an absurd co-op roguelite for all ages, full of wacky situations. Get ready for some Fu-lish action!

Wishlist FUFUFU on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2025050/FUFUFU/
Follow FUFUFU on Twitter: https://twitter.com/FUFUFU_THE_GAME
